  Source:
    Title: The Wonders of the Holy Name
Tags:
  - 1036
  - 1017
---
The Name of Jesus is the shortest, the easiest and the most powerful of
prayers. Everyone can say it even in the midst of his daily work. God cannot
refuse to hear it.
